{"tid":1650344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：香港經濟下行風險比沙士和金融海嘯時更嚴峻","createTime":"2019-10-13T02:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:00:05.000Z","uid":212626,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"e6bb4f9a1216bcdeedf270ad742e5cccd589fade","tid":1650344,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗表示，期望立法會星期三復會後，可以順利展開工作，盡快處理大量積壓的法案和撥款建議，尤其與市民福祉息息相關的法案和撥款建議。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗在網誌中稱，立法會仍在審議的15項條例草案中，涵蓋不少民生項目，希望盡快處理。另外約有740億元與工程有關的撥款，以及政府在8月中推出的紓困措施，都等待財委會審批。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，不少建造業界人士擔憂工程撥款無期，工程不足令建築工人開工不足，影響生計。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港正處於外憂內患，經濟下行風險，看來比沙士和金融海嘯時更嚴峻，面對極大壓力</span>。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又稱，復會當日行政長官林鄭月娥會宣讀新一份《施政報告》，會致力處理深層次的社會問題，並以改善民生為主軸。之後保安局長李家超會宣布正式撤回修訂逃犯條例，過程不涉及投票或辯論。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，政府會以開放態度，繼續細心聆聽和考慮各方意見，改善施政，<span style=\"color: red;\">懇請議員確保立法會有秩序、有效率和暢順地運作，避免香港停滯不前</span>。香港不能長期處於目前的不穩定狀態，需要廣大市民的支持，以及各方通力合作，才能共同走出困局。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2274261/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2274261%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=70d4d137\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2274261/</a>"},{"pid":"3ec9858415a2409db1113c162543aa94f83765fd","tid":1650344,"uid":290118,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上行嗰陣又無人分享到，是但啦"},{"pid":"432f95d3f1778914fcbdf2ead2d5e8a11d3254aa","tid":1650344,"uid":63,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"no stake"},{"pid":"2f97be1cd6ec74802f1369f91d77730de2718669","tid":1650344,"uid":63,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ec9858415a2409db1113c162543aa94f83765fd","tid":1650344,"uid":290118,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上行嗰陣又無人分享到，是但啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"反而下行分享到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae977fd29639980605002be29b664f7c147b961a","tid":1650344,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗表示，期望立法會星期三復會後，可以順利展開工作，盡快處理大量積壓的法案和撥款建議，尤其與<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>市民</del>收成期</span>福祉息息相關的法案和撥款建議。"},{"pid":"afdebab2777bffe16aeb9ece4a8de61adbe8960b","tid":1650344,"uid":2230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"望番樓價先出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dcfa2ac8bffe0a43d15d9c46aa7e1ce4162450","tid":1650344,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28d529c6b90088943b56efb1bfb01b9ad79eb8e6","tid":1650344,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"9up"},{"pid":"46dc0805b88939797005bfef62b6994b5868f2d9","tid":1650344,"uid":82375,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"下行係因為你地班香港政府官員癈 d外資要撒"},{"pid":"2505766e7566af19978311a7fbe4e4618632a37b","tid":1650344,"uid":8858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"沙士食飯幾錢，依家幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2833d4a9615baf823107800afdef1ec609aa8be","tid":1650344,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"afdebab2777bffe16aeb9ece4a8de61adbe8960b","tid":1650344,"uid":2230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"望番樓價先出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl